    "syllabus": {
        "zh": "1. 越南語字母、音調、拼字與發音<br>2. 數字<br>3. 日常生活會話<br>4. 文法<br>5. 越南文化",
        "en": "1. Introduction of Vietnamese alphabets, tones, spelling and pronunciation.<br>2. How to say numbers using Vietnamese.<br>3. How to use Vietnamese language in daily conversation regarding to relationships.<br>4. Vietnamese grammar in use.<br>5. Understand of Vietnamese culture.<br>"
